{"lemma":"شِيَعُ","slug":"شِيَعُ","root":"ش.#.ع","root_slug":"ش-_-ع","root_link":"/words/roots/ش-_-ع","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"شِيعَة","root":"شيع","pos":"N","occurrence_count":11},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":5},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n23525","n23535"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%B4%D9%90%D9%8A%D9%8E%D8%B9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"cult, sect"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"followers, assistants","tags":["collective"],"examples":[{"text":"وَدَخَلَ الْمَدِينَةَ عَلَىٰ حِينِ غَفْلَةٍ مِّنْ أَهْلِهَا فَوَجَدَ فِيهَا رَجُلَيْنِ يَقْتَتِلَانِ هَـٰذَا مِن شِيعَتِهِ وَهَـٰذَا مِنْ عَدُوِّهِ ۖ فَاسْتَغَاثَهُ الَّذِي مِن شِيعَتِهِ عَلَى الَّذِي مِنْ عَدُوِّهِ فَوَكَزَهُ مُوسَىٰ فَقَضَىٰ عَلَيْهِ ۖ قَالَ هَـٰذَا مِنْ عَمَلِ الشَّيْطَانِ ۖ إِنَّهُ عَدُوٌّ مُّضِلٌّ مُّبِينٌ","english":"[One day] he entered the city at a time when its people were not likely to take notice. He found there two men fighting, this one from among his followers, and that one from his enemies. The one who was from his followers sought his help against him who was from his enemies. So Moses hit him with his fist, whereupon he expired. He said, ‘This is of Satan’s doing. Indeed he is clearly a misguiding enemy.’"}]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"adherents, disciples, partisans","tags":["collective"]},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"faction, party"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"the Shi'a","tags":["definite"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Compare شَاعَ (šāʕa, “to spread (intransitive), to become known”). Cognate with Hebrew סיעה (si'a, “party, faction”)."},"ipa":["/ʃiː.ʕa/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n23525","headword_ar":"شَيْعٌ","root":"$yE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A space"},{"kind":"text","text":"[of time]. (S, O, K.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aqaAma fulaAnN $ahorFA A^awo $ayoEahu","text_ar":"اَقَامَ فُلَانٌ شَهْرًا اَوْ شَيْعَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Such a one remained,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stayed, a month or the space thereof:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nearly the space thereof."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=tiyka gadFA A^awo $ayoEahu","text_ar":"ا=تِيكَ غَدًا اَوْ شَيْعَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will come to thee to-morrow or after it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to-morrow or the day after it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h`*aA $ayoEu h`*aA","text_ar":"هٰذَا شَيْعُ هٰذَا"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"This is he that was born next after this;"},{"kind":"text","text":"like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$awoEuhu","text_ar":"شَوْعُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, K, all in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$wE","text_ar":"شوع"},{"kind":"text","text":":) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"this is the like of this."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, O and K in the present art.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ayoEN","text_ar":"شَيْعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A follower:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a friend,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a comrade,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"an assistant."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A lion's whelp:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, IDrd, S, O, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"when he has attained to taking prey;"},{"kind":"text","text":"so in the L: and some say the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"lion"},{"kind":"text","text":"[himself]. (TA.)       -A2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAy^iEN","text_ar":"شَايِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","O","K","Lth","IDrd"]},{"entry_id":"n23535","headword_ar":"شَيِّعٌ","root":"$yE","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A sharer,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"partner:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$uyaEaA='u","text_ar":"شُيَعَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K, TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humo $uyaEaA='u fiyhaA","text_ar":"هُمْ شُيَعَا=ءُ فِيهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They are sharers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"partners, in it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. a house ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daAr","text_ar":"دَار"},{"kind":"text","text":") or land;] i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"every one of them is a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$ay~iE","text_ar":"شَيِّع"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to his fellow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fellows"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (O, K.) And ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"humaA muta$aAyiEaAni","text_ar":"هُمَا مُتَشَايِعَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY daArK","text_ar":"فِى دَارٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, K,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aroDK","text_ar":"اَرْضٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (O;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$otaAEaAni","text_ar":"مُشْتَاعَانِ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O, TA,) in the copies of the K, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muta$aAEaAni","text_ar":"مُتَشَاعَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"They two are sharers,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"partners, in a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land."},{"kind":"text","text":"(O.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aAru $ay~iEapN bayonahumo","text_ar":"الدَّارُ شَيِّعَةٌ بَيْنَهُمْ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The house is undivided"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"shared"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"among them;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn. ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mu$aAEapN","text_ar":"مُشَاعَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (O, K. [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aAy^iEN","text_ar":"شَايِعٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["TA","O","K"]}]}}